## 十、CSS Override 参考（补充到 el-overrides.css）

```css
/* ===== Select Trigger ===== */
.el-select .el-input__wrapper {
  height: 36px;
  padding: 0 12px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);     /* 4px */
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #dedfe3 inset;
}

.el-select .el-input__wrapper:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--pcv-brand) inset;
}

.el-select .el-input.is-focus .el-input__wrapper {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--pcv-brand) inset;
}

.el-select .el-input.is-disabled .el-input__wrapper {
  background-color: #f4f5f6;
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #dedfe3 inset;
}

/* Small size */
.el-select.el-select--small .el-input__wrapper {
  height: 32px;
}

/* Placeholder */
.el-select .el-input__placeholder,
.el-select .el-input__inner::placeholder {
  color: #b2b2b8;
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* Selected value text */
.el-select .el-input__inner {
  color: #66666c;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 20px;
}

/* Arrow icon color */
.el-select .el-input__suffix .el-icon {
  color: #b2b2b8;
}
.el-select:hover .el-input__suffix .el-icon,
.el-select .el-input.is-focus .el-input__suffix .el-icon {
  color: var(--pcv-brand);
}

/* Error state */
.el-select .el-input.is-error .el-input__wrapper {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #ea5455 inset;
}
.el-select .el-input.is-error .el-input__inner {
  color: #ea5455;
}

/* ===== Select Options ===== */
.el-select-dropdown__item {
  height: 40px;
  padding: 10px 12px;               /* Note: 12px left padding (not 20px like el-dropdown) */
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 20px;
  color: #66666c;
}

.el-select-dropdown__item:hover:not(.is-disabled) {
  background: rgba(var(--pcv-brand-rgb), 0.15);   /* 15% — deeper than command dropdown's 5% */
  color: #66666c;
}

.el-select-dropdown__item.selected,
.el-select-dropdown__item.is-selected {
  color: var(--pcv-brand);
  font-weight: 500;
  background: transparent;
}

/* Multi-select checkbox in option */
.el-select-dropdown__item.is-selected::after {
  display: none;                    /* Remove EP's default checkmark */
}

/* ===== Multi-select Tags ===== */
.el-select .el-tag {
  height: 22px;
  border-radius: var(--radius-full);
  margin: 2px;
}
.el-select .el-tag .el-icon {
  font-size: 14px;
}
```

